{"tid":2444681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅根未罷休 向OFCOM投訴名嘴摩根 惟哈里夫婦在英支持度創新低","createTime":"2021-03-13T04:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T05:58:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2523803f91750c35e71ba3b388ff9455f03739d9","tid":2444681,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"英國哈里王子及妻子梅根的專訪播出後，英國名嘴摩根（Piers Morgan）表明不認同並連環炮轟梅根，遭大舉投訴後辭職。梅根未肯罷休，向英國通訊管理局（Ofcom）作正式投訴。不過，英國人對於哈里夫婦的觀感也越來越差，根據最新調查顯示，二人的支持度創下新低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210313/FWDCDU6J4NED3EGHPZR5RANKTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210313%2FFWDCDU6J4NED3EGHPZR5RANKTE%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=28ba477d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210313%2FFWDCDU6J4NED3EGHPZR5RANKTE%2F&h=75147ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210313/FWDCDU6J4NED3EGHPZR5RANKTE/</a>"},{"pid":"8730fbd89781ec4469b8a6648c4edbca841bf345","tid":2444681,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3044dec4315387a3fdfb2ee37b1b89cb775b542","tid":2444681,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7175da85f8ef25d41bd7c7b844b903381f5850dd","tid":2444681,"uid":42762,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk